swinging a golf club

38:25.606 --> 38:27.608
in a fit of rage.

38:27.641 --> 38:29.510
Do I think he did?

38:29.543 --> 38:30.944
No.

38:30.977 --> 38:33.113
Who's your suspect, then?

38:33.146 --> 38:34.848
Have you looked
at his wife?

38:34.881 --> 38:38.752
You think she would kill
her own daughter?

38:38.785 --> 38:42.956
I think anybody's capable
of swinging a golf club

38:42.989 --> 38:44.825
in a fit of rage.

38:44.858 --> 38:47.561
Why did you
and Mr. Littlefield

38:47.594 --> 38:48.929
end your affair?

38:48.962 --> 38:52.032
