will please rise.

39:17.691 --> 39:19.025
Mr. Foreman,

39:19.059 --> 39:23.496
the jury has reached
a unanimous verdict?

39:23.530 --> 39:25.866
We have, your honor.

39:25.899 --> 39:27.534
What say you?

39:27.568 --> 39:29.536
Commonwealth vs. Bruce Wilson

39:29.570 --> 39:32.438
on the count of rape
of a child under 12.

39:32.472 --> 39:34.908
We find the defendant
Bruce Wilson...

39:37.477 --> 39:38.645
guilty.

39:40.681 --> 39:42.916
JUDGE: Members of the jury,
this completes your service.

39:42.949 --> 39:45.085
You're dismissed
with the thanks of the court.

39:45.118 --> 39:47.654
Security, please take
the defendant into custody.

39:47.688 --> 39:50.657
We'll see you on March the 20th
for sentencing,

39:50.691 --> 39:53.026
and we're adjourned.

40:01.568 --> 40:03.937
We'll need
a victim impact statement

40:03.970 --> 40:06.006
