41:27.888 --> 41:30.023
It's pretty much a scientific
certainty, Raymond.

41:30.056 --> 41:31.792
They will now be able
to prove

41:31.825 --> 41:34.194
you were there
and you had sex with her.

41:34.227 --> 41:36.229
The game is over, Raymond.

41:36.262 --> 41:38.699
If I have any chance--
any chance at all

41:38.732 --> 41:40.867
